                q: "10g of ice at 0C, 20g of water at 20C and \\( m \\) g of steam at 100C are mixed in a calorimeter. If the final temperature is 40C, what is \\( m \\)? (\\( L_v = 540 \\text{ cal/g}, L_f = 80 \\text{ cal/g}, s_w = 1 \\text{ cal/g}^\\circ\\text{C} \\))",
